src:
Dawn is filthy rich in 'Money' MV
05 Nov 2019, 09:23 by germainej
Dawn has dropped his music video for "Money"!In the MV,Dawn is filthy rich in what looks to be a post-apocalyptic world. "Money" is about not being able to live without something, and it's the former Pentagon member's first release as an artist under P-Nation.Watch Dawn's "Money" MV above, and let us know what you think in the comments below.
